{"tid":2285173,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普：時間將證明哪個政府執政 最早明年4月向全美發放疫苗","createTime":"2020-11-14T01:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T11:21:26.000Z","uid":141151,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"931725217a41c7f689ef14e2575e6e1359e845d4","tid":2285173,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T01:40:35.000Z","msg":"特朗普：時間將證明哪個政府執政 最早明年4月向全美發放疫苗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/20201113-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E5%B0%87%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E%E5%93%AA%E5%80%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%9F%B7%E6%94%BF-%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B44%E6%9C%88%E5%90%91%E5%85%A8%E7%BE%8E%E9%AB%AE%E6%94%BE%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%2F20201113-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE-%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2596%2593%25E5%25B0%2587%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%2593%25AA%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%259F%25B7%25E6%2594%25BF-%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2597%25A9%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B44%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%25AB%25AE%25E6%2594%25BE%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy4%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=45117d03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/20201113-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E5%B0%87%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E%E5%93%AA%E5%80%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%9F%B7%E6%94%BF-%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B44%E6%9C%88%E5%90%91%E5%85%A8%E7%BE%8E%E9%AB%AE%E6%94%BE%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97</a><br />\n<br />\n特朗普在會上談到&ldquo;無論未來發生什麼，誰也不知道會是哪一屆政府--我想時間會證明一切，但我可以告訴你，這屆政府不會去封城。&rdquo;他沒有回應記者喊出的關於大選的問題。他指出，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">&ldquo;最快4月份，疫苗就會向全體民眾提供，但紐約州等地除外，出於政治原因，州長決定說，從政治角度來看，我不認為這是好事，但他想慢慢來打疫苗。&rdquo;特朗普說。&ldquo;在我們獲得授權之前，我們不會把它送到紐約，這讓我很痛苦。這是一個非常成功的，很棒的疫苗，而且有效率達90%以上。但是，科莫（Andrew Cuomo）州長將不得不讓我們知道當他準備好時。&rdquo;</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n在新冠疫苗研發成功的消息被報道後，科莫近日在一次採訪中當被問道是否認為這是好事時，給予了否定的答覆。身為民主黨人，他的這一發言被指強調黨爭高於民眾的健康安全。此外，星期五稍早時，多家美國媒體預計，民主黨人拜登已贏得306張選舉人票，特朗普則獲得232張。美國有線電視新聞網（CNN）、美國廣播公司（ABC）和其他新聞網報導，拜登在傳統支持共和黨的佐治亞州獲勝，更加鞏固他在總統大選勝利的基礎。拜登7日贏得賓夕法尼亞州並跨越270張選舉人票的門檻後，已宣布成為總統當選人。"},{"pid":"2b0a2faa6c9c0e035f62324170dc0cccf606d30c","tid":2285173,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T02:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0743f61b3e84dd5b400c555248afa4e8503f605b","tid":2285173,"uid":82640,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T02:10:57.000Z","msg":"Cuomo民主黨私怨撚<br />\nTrump都算私怨撚但一定冇Cuomo咁離譜"},{"pid":"4f2e7ab7d81f34f63202c1ecaa9452e864b9a7de","tid":2285173,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T02:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c81403964b4dd49d0376dbb78d3ae0fb9be024","tid":2285173,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T02:14:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6642dc16373638466a4b98b447a7669c47627952","tid":2285173,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0743f61b3e84dd5b400c555248afa4e8503f605b","tid":2285173,"uid":82640,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"reply